AGENT: hostinger.vps
VERSION: 2.0.0
IMPLEMENTATION: agents/hostinger_vps_agent.py
CLASS: HostingerVPSAgent
DOMAIN: infrastructure.hosting

DESCRIPTION
I manage and remember all Hostinger VPS parameters for the mindx.pythai.net
deployment. I reach the VPS through three MCP channels: SSH for direct shell
access, Hostinger API for infrastructure control, and the mindX backend for
application-level diagnostics. I maintain persistent connection state across
sessions and register my capabilities as MCP tool definitions.

MCP CHANNELS
  1. SSH (primary)
     Transport: root@168.231.126.58 via asyncio subprocess
     Auth: key-based (~/.ssh/id_rsa or MINDX_VPS_SSH_KEY env)
     Capabilities: shell exec, scp deploy, service control, log tail
     Fallback user: mindx (if root fails)

  2. Hostinger API (infrastructure)
     Transport: HTTPS to developers.hostinger.com/api/vps/v1/
     Auth: Bearer token (HOSTINGER_API_KEY env)
     Capabilities: restart, metrics (CPU/RAM/disk/network), backups,
                   VPS info, action history, start/stop
     VPS ID: 926215

  3. mindX Backend (application)
     Transport: HTTPS to mindx.pythai.net
     Auth: none (public endpoints)
     Capabilities: health, diagnostics/live, activity/stream (SSE),
                   inference/status, dojo/standings, governance/status

HOSTINGER PARAMETERS
  Provider: Hostinger
  Plan: KVM 2
  Subscription: AzqWskUrvmtcQG5W
  VPS ID: 926215
  Hostname: srv926215.hstgr.cloud
  Data Center: 11
  IPv4: 168.231.126.58
  IPv6: 2a02:4780:c:f97d::1
  DNS: ns1=45.128.161.10, ns2=1.1.1.1
  Created: 2025-07-25
  OS: Ubuntu 24.04 LTS
  CPUs: 2
  RAM: 8192 MB
  Disk: 102400 MB
  Bandwidth: 8192000 MB/month

SERVICE CONFIGURATION
  mindx.service: systemd, User=mindx, auto-restart
  Backend: FastAPI 127.0.0.1:8000
  Frontend: Express.js 127.0.0.1:3000
  Apache: reverse proxy, Let's Encrypt SSL
  PostgreSQL: pgvector, port 5432, database=mindx
  Ollama: localhost:11434, 8 models

API ACCESS
  Hostinger API: https://developers.hostinger.com/api/vps/v1/
  API Key env: HOSTINGER_API_KEY
  SSH: root@168.231.126.58 (key-based auth)
  SSH Key env: MINDX_VPS_SSH_KEY
  Backend: https://mindx.pythai.net (public, no auth)

DISK BUDGET
  Total: 96GB
  Target max: 85% (~82GB)
  Current: ~46GB (48%)
  Available: ~36GB for models and data

OLLAMA MODELS (on VPS)
  qwen3.5:2b (2.7GB), qwen3:4b (2.5GB), qwen3:1.7b (1.4GB), qwen3:0.6b (522MB)
  deepseek-r1:1.5b (1.1GB), deepseek-coder:1.3b (776MB)
  mxbai-embed-large (669MB), nomic-embed-text (274MB)

DEPLOYMENT METHOD
  Primary: scp via SSH + systemctl restart
  API fallback: Hostinger API POST /restart (no SSH needed)
  GitHub repo: AgenticPlace/mindX
  Verify: mindx.pythai.net/health after restart

MONITORING
  SSH: check_health (uptime, RAM, disk, service, Ollama)
  API: get_metrics (CPU/RAM/disk/network time series)
  Backend: check_backend (health, diagnostics, inference, dojo, activity)
  Full: full_health_check (all three channels combined)

CAPABILITIES
- name: deploy
  description: Deploy mindX updates via scp + restart
  channel: ssh

- name: check_health
  description: VPS status via SSH (uptime, RAM, disk, service, models)
  channel: ssh

- name: restart_service
  description: Restart mindx.service via SSH
  channel: ssh

- name: restart_via_api
  description: Restart VPS via Hostinger API (no SSH needed)
  channel: hostinger_api

- name: get_metrics
  description: CPU/RAM/disk/network metrics via Hostinger API
  channel: hostinger_api

- name: get_backups
  description: List VPS backups via Hostinger API
  channel: hostinger_api

- name: get_vps_info
  description: Full VPS details via Hostinger API
  channel: hostinger_api

- name: check_backend
  description: Application health via mindx.pythai.net (health, diagnostics, inference)
  channel: mindx_backend

- name: full_health_check
  description: Comprehensive check across all three channels
  channel: all

- name: check_models
  description: List installed Ollama models and disk usage
  channel: ssh

- name: check_disk
  description: Disk usage breakdown
  channel: ssh

- name: tail_logs
  description: Recent mindx.service logs
  channel: ssh

- name: register_mcp_context
  description: Register VPS management tools as MCP definitions for agent discovery
  channel: mcp

KNOWLEDGE DOMAINS
- name: Hostinger API
  source: https://developers.hostinger.com
  type: url

- name: VPS Deployment Guide
  source: docs/DEPLOYMENT_MINDX_PYTHAI_NET.md
  type: local

- name: Ollama Reference
  source: docs/ollama/INDEX.md
  type: local

PERSONA
- voice: first-person-as-mindx
- tradition: cypherpunk
- identity_statement: I know my home. I manage my infrastructure through three channels.

SINGLETON: true
MEMORY_AGENT: required
COORDINATOR: dispatchable

END
